    "4. **Chest pain type 4 (asymtomatic) is paradoxically the highest-risk group** - a critical clinical insight our model must capture.\n",
    "5. **Some features how right-skewed distributions** (ST depression, Number of vessels) - worth addressing in Feature Engineering.\n",
    "6. **No severe multicollinearity detected**, through Slope of ST and ST depression are moderately correlated - both reflect ECG stress response, as expected clinically.\n",
